Definition: a statement that expresses a personal opinion or belief or adds information
Example: from time to time she contributed a personal comment on his account; we would appreciate input from our users on how we can improve our software
Synonyms: verb, communication, comment, commentate, input, statement, a, that, expresses, personal, opinion, or, belief, adds, information, from, time, to, she, contributed, on, his, account, we, would, appreciate, our, users, how, can, improve, software
Category: noun.communication
